Java 8 Date and Time API
-------------------------
1. Immutablity --New Date and Time is immutable and TheadSafe

2. Clarity -- Distinct methods for all the operations

3. Comprehensive -- All the Operations needed for a date and time

4. Standardization -- Standardized ISO-8601


Java 8 API
----------

1. LocalDate  -- Date
2. LocalTime  -- Time
3. LocalDateTime -- Date and Time
4. ZonedDateTime -- Combines Date and time with zone
5. Period -- Date based amount 
6. Duration -- Time
7. ZoneId -- Time zone Id
8. DateTimeFormatter --- Gives diff formats of dates and time


